Requirements List - GlobalMart

Functional Requirements

| ID | Requirement | Description |
|----|-------------|-------------|
| FR1 | User Registration | Users can create account with email/phone |
| FR2 | User Login | Users can log in with credentials |
| FR3 | Browse Products | Users can view products by category |
| FR4 | Product Search | Users can search for products by keyword |
| FR5 | Multi-currency Display | Products show prices in selected currency |
| FR6 | Shopping Cart | Users can add/remove items from cart |
| FR7 | Wishlist | Users can save products to wishlist |
| FR8 | Price Comparison | Users can compare prices across sellers |
| FR9 | Checkout | Users can proceed to checkout with cart items |
| FR10 | Payment Simulation | Users can simulate payment (no real money) |
| FR11 | Order History | Users can view past orders |
| FR12 | Logistics Tracking | Users can track shipping status |
| FR13 | User Reviews | Users can leave product reviews |
| FR14 | Seller Information | Users can view seller details and ratings |
| FR15 | Language Toggle | Users can switch between English and Chinese |

Non-Functional Requirements

| ID | Requirement | Description |
|----|-------------|-------------|
| NFR1 | Performance | Page load time under 3 seconds |
| NFR2 | Usability | Interface must be intuitive for international users |
| NFR3 | Security | User data encrypted; secure login |
| NFR4 | Reliability | System uptime 99% |
| NFR5 | Scalability | Should handle up to 1000 concurrent users |
| NFR6 | Compatibility | Works on Chrome, Firefox, Safari |
| NFR7 | Maintainability | Code should be modular and well-documented |
